## Copy this file to `local.properties` and fill in your real values.
## `local.properties` is git-ignored, so your secrets won't be committed.

## Location of the Android SDK (required)
sdk.dir=/path/to/Android/Sdk

## Bugly crash reporting AppID (optional)
## Get yours at https://bugly.qq.com after creating an Android product.
## If left empty, crash reporting is disabled (BuildConfig.BUGLY_APP_ID == "").
BUGLY_APP_ID=